{"tid":1843404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本京都出現標語：「恐怖中国人不要來」　","createTime":"2020-01-26T07:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T06:43:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":675,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"dc718af9ebe8379010f82f8da1ab8dbed9850906","tid":1843404,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.ctwant.com/images/cover/34/34434/sm-d129396d2eaf7908da0a724bdd139a21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ctwant.com%2Fimages%2Fcover%2F34%2F34434%2Fsm-d129396d2eaf7908da0a724bdd139a21.jpg&h=cd51f06d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸武漢肺炎疫情擴散各地，本來就不喜歡陸客種種行為的日本民眾，繼日前有日本商店張貼「中國人種進入商店禁止」標語後，昨（25）日在京都極負盛名的觀光景點清水寺外街道，赫然再度出現中英文夾雜的標語，強烈表達不歡迎吵鬧的大陸恐怖觀光客，更不歡迎會帶來（肺炎）感染的中國人，再次引發網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ctwant.com/images/content/34/34434/6a9e7ad24853aa3e7cff9f9d7a0e1e1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ctwant.com%2Fimages%2Fcontent%2F34%2F34434%2F6a9e7ad24853aa3e7cff9f9d7a0e1e1d.jpg&h=309c1711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n京都的清水寺跟金閣寺一樣，都是當地極具代表性的觀光景點，每天觀光人潮滿滿，但近來因大陸武漢肺炎造成日本民眾恐慌，京都當地民眾都自覺地戴上口罩，以防被外來的大陸旅客感染。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ctwant.com/images/content/34/34434/6d2f1ed02d41ae383f3c99eaeb1b6645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ctwant.com%2Fimages%2Fcontent%2F34%2F34434%2F6d2f1ed02d41ae383f3c99eaeb1b6645.jpg&h=027c51e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨天有台灣旅客在清水寺外的主要街道上，赫然看見一張抗議中國大陸遊客的標語，上面寫著「 overtourists  are  terrorists 」、「noisy foreigners  go  out 」及「大聲說的中國人不來」等三行電腦列印的中英文，最下方又有一行明顯是手寫後補上去的中文「不要來感染中国」。<br />\n<br />\n這張被台灣遊客發現的標語，不論是中文或英文，儘管在文句用語上並不通暢，卻能讓人感受到書寫者心中的不滿，而在此之前，由於本月16日在日本出現首宗武漢肺炎病例，患者就是一名住在神奈川縣30多歲的中國男子，雖然該男子已病癒出院，但日本民間已對陸客更恐懼，本月21日一家在神奈川縣箱根的店家，就在門口用紅字寫下「中國人種進入商店禁止」的告示牌，如今在京都又出現同樣排斥大陸人的標語，再次引發爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ctwant.com/article/34434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctwant.com%2Farticle%2F34434&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGegwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=c409a85b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctwant.com/article/34434</a>"},{"pid":"57b0122e802be72251a3fe89caaf76efe85de513","tid":1843404,"uid":71341,"like":17,"dislike":880,"score":-863,"citedBy":27,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:50:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"997ca16ec77acaa2775d6f76a0b9d2571517966d","tid":1843404,"uid":264245,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"呢d先係正常既反應<br />\n<br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"7d03c949639e2d9cf1c451f2530ea5f9e6c4b7c7","tid":1843404,"uid":290118,"like":272,"dislike":2,"score":270,"quote":{"pid":"57b0122e802be72251a3fe89caaf76efe85de513","tid":1843404,"uid":71341,"like":17,"dislike":880,"score":-863,"citedBy":27,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:50:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"返中国啦你"},{"pid":"60df0e5eb16edeb4fcb4d5dc19602bb889eb26ff","tid":1843404,"uid":184679,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"quote":{"pid":"57b0122e802be72251a3fe89caaf76efe85de513","tid":1843404,"uid":71341,"like":17,"dislike":880,"score":-863,"citedBy":27,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:50:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"即係你做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d0a8ac3af997c35b331ae95d308a74e1e35689","tid":1843404,"uid":61923,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"57b0122e802be72251a3fe89caaf76efe85de513","tid":1843404,"uid":71341,"like":17,"dislike":880,"score":-863,"citedBy":27,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:50:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"你咪係中国隻狗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd432aee1f5e2f3b6874a6335f670de8f66af7c","tid":1843404,"uid":38904,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score"