Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:55:22.000Z","msg":"全部支那人都係習狗隻狗"},{"pid":"8354bb6584a2aa3a8bbe63ddc9736559e320c6da","tid":1843404,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0Njtom.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0Njtom.jpg&h=fdbb1106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4Zahjj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4Zahjj.gif&h=03d0ab77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3708b7d0878849ed7820c86cbe36b12a78b5f19","tid":1843404,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc718af9ebe8379010f82f8da1ab8dbed9850906","tid":1843404,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.ctwant.com/images/cover/34/34434/sm-d129396d2eaf7908da0a724bdd139a21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ctwant.com%2Fimages%2Fcover%2F34%2F34434%2Fsm-d129396d2eaf7908da0a724bdd139a21.jpg&h=cd51f06d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸武漢肺炎疫情擴散各地，本來就不喜歡陸客種種行為的日本民眾，繼日前有日本商店張貼「中國人種進入商店禁止」標語後，昨（25）日在京都極負盛名的觀光景點清水寺外街道，赫然再度出現中英文夾雜的標語，強烈表達不歡迎吵鬧的大陸恐怖觀光客，更不歡迎會帶來（肺炎）感染的中國人，再次引發網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ctwant.com/images/content/34/34434/6a9e7ad24853aa3e7cff9f9d7a0e1e1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ctwant.com%2Fimages%2Fcontent%2F34%2F34434%2F6a9e7ad24853aa3e7cff9f9d7a0e1e1d.jpg&h=309c1711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n京都的清水寺跟金閣寺一樣，都是當地極具代表性的觀光景點，每天觀光人潮滿滿，但近來因大陸武漢肺炎造成日本民眾恐慌，京都當地民眾都自覺地戴上口罩，以防被外來的大陸旅客感染。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ctwant.com/images/content/34/34434/6d2f1ed02d41ae383f3c99eaeb1b6645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ctwant.com%2Fimages%2Fcontent%2F34%2F34434%2F6d2f1ed02d41ae383f3c99eaeb1b6645.jpg&h=027c51e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨天有台灣旅客在清水寺外的主要街道上，赫然看見一張抗議中國大陸遊客的標語，上面寫著「 overtourists  are  terrorists 」、「noisy foreigners  go  out 」及「大聲說的中國人不來」等三行電腦列印的中英文，最下方又有一行明顯是手寫後補上去的中文「不要來感染中国」。<br />\n<br />\n這張被台灣遊客發現的標語，不論是中文或英文，儘管在文句用語上並不通暢，卻能讓人感受到書寫者心中的不滿，而在此之前，由於本月16日在日本出現首宗武漢肺炎病例，患者就是一名住在神奈川縣30多歲的中國男子，雖然該男子已病癒出院，但日本民間已對陸客更恐懼，本月21日一家在神奈川縣箱根的店家，就在門口用紅字寫下「中國人種進入商店禁止」的告示牌，如今在京都又出現同樣排斥大陸人的標語，再次引發爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ctwant.com/article/34434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctwant.com%2Farticle%2F34434&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGegwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=c409a85b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctwant.com/article/34434</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"Google translate?錯曬"},{"pid":"14972a6b7f26dc842e4e47bf3bed92726f3d6cf7","tid":1843404,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3uQQGdW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3uQQGdW.png&h=64ab3017&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfd8412555eb15d5db9ec41b605704514ab7d875","tid":1843404,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:26:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/yoshiefans/status/1221679445334876161?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyoshiefans%2Fstatus%2F1221679445334876161%3Fs%3D21&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGegwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=b73892aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyoshiefans%2Fstatus%2F1221679445334876161%3Fs%3D21&h=78bf10b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/yoshiefans/status/1221679445334876161?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n即做tweet<br />\n不過佢哋做乜用繁體字<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyoOsYz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtyoOsYz.png&h=07e8ac4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j6HzowV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6Hzo